# local env files (secrets). `.env.example` and `.env.production` are kept
# tracked on purpose: `.env.production` holds only the non-secret public
# NEXT_PUBLIC_API_BASE_URL that is baked into the client bundle at build time.
# Put anything secret in `.env.local` / `.env.production.local` (ignored below).
.env*.local
.env

